sub_title: Advisor Sustainable Economic Development at Royal Tropical Institute
summary:
In the course of my international work and living experience, I gained a lot from having come across many interesting and inspiring people. Equity, justice, fairness and inclusion are guiding principles in listening to their stories. I always look for opportunities, and when I encounter difficulties or problems, I search for creative solutions. 

Work experience in: Ghana, Senegal, The Gambia, India, Kenya, Uganda, Tanzania, Malaysia, Myanmar, Nepal, The Netherlands, United Kingdom

Specialties: project management, project coordination, qualitative evaluation, knowledge documentation
